data.text:
Tom Jones: Live in Australia

Arguably one of the most successful vocalists of the modern age, Welsh sensation Tom Jones is a world-class performer, having recorded hit songs in almost every genre of popular music over the past 60 years - from pop to rock, R&B to show tunes, country, dance, soul and gospel - selling over 100 million records in the process. This rarely seen concert features a set list of classic hits.
